{
  "texts": [
    "A total of 37 users took part in the interviews, of which more than half of the participants were male (approx. 57%).",
    "The age of most participants fell between 18 and 24 (approx.",
    "62%), and a considerable number of respondents were between the ages of 25 and 35.",
    "The participants were primarily students; 10 were undergraduate students, 6 were graduates, and 3 were postgraduate students/ doctoral students.",
    "Two participants had jobs in the industry."
  ]
}